simplesect.title: Xlib Compose Keys for iso8859-2
simplesect.para: Applications using Xlib input handling should recognize these compose key sequences in locales using the iso8859-2 compose table.
ISO 8859-2 (Latin2) Compose Sequence Sequence Definition <Multi_key> Means <Compose> Special Character

row.entry: Right-hand side (Accented Alphabet) These compose sequences are pure supposition on my part. It would be nice to know what the real cultural conventions are for compose sequences.
